Neither of the two are listed in the search engines I have used to check to see if the name is on the Vietnam wall.<br><br>
I have often been frustrated by looking for someone I though had only been wounded to find them listed on the wall. others who I though killed, were listed only as wounded.<br><br>
I have I have not added to your pain, but perhaps to your hope. After 30 years I found a buddie of mine I though had been killed in Nam what a great feeling that was.<br><br>
Welcome home bro<br><br>
